278
00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:04,240
Maintaining public order
and upholding the norms of society

279
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:06,240
are also part of our job as police officers.

280
00:15:07,390 --> 00:15:09,270
So you are officially appointed mediators.

281
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,790
No wonder so many major and important cases

282
00:15:10,790 --> 00:15:11,870
end up unresolved.

283
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,390
We accept your criticism

284
00:15:21,790 --> 00:15:23,120
and shall actively make improvements.

285
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:26,550
There is a serious and important case

286
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,360
that we need to consult with you about.

287
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:41,480
This girl's name is Chen Yuan.

288
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:44,150
She died from overdosing several months ago.

289
00:15:46,030 --> 00:15:47,000
She's your alumna.

290
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:54,790
I'm sorry.

291
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,320
Her death was quite odd.

292
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:59,240
She contacted her classmate

293
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:01,510
named Cui Ying two weeks before her death.

294
00:16:02,230 --> 00:16:03,900
She passed some important evidence

295
00:16:03,900 --> 00:16:05,540
about the drug traffickers
in Xiaxi District to Cui Ying.

296
00:16:06,470 --> 00:16:07,900
We've talked to this girl.

297
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:09,990
She submitted the evidence

298
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:11,510
and also mentioned you.

299
00:16:14,580 --> 00:16:15,510
She said

300
00:16:15,780 --> 00:16:18,230
she once told you about Chen Yuan.

301
00:16:18,780 --> 00:16:20,470
But you stopped her from reporting to the police.

302
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:22,060
Do you recall that?

303
00:16:22,660 --> 00:16:23,270
Yes.

304
00:16:25,230 --> 00:16:26,750
I did watch the video.

305
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,540
It made my blood run cold.

306
00:16:29,110 --> 00:16:30,540
But who should I report it to?

307
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:31,870
As far as I know,

308
00:16:31,870 --> 00:16:33,820
Jin Zaihong, who appeared in the video,

309
00:16:34,150 --> 00:16:35,780
and Deputy Director Cui Hongliang
of Xiaxi District

310
00:16:35,780 --> 00:16:36,660
are closely acquainted.

311
00:16:36,900 --> 00:16:38,300
And I'm only an ordinary person.

312
00:16:38,780 --> 00:16:39,820
I don't have that much influence.

313
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:41,990
Is it wrong to protect myself

314
00:16:44,030 --> 00:16:45,060
from danger?

315
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:49,150
Not at all.

316
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:50,870
I understand.

317
00:16:51,990 --> 00:16:52,940
As an attorney,

318
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:54,390
you do know what's good for you.

319
00:16:55,420 --> 00:16:57,110
I just don't get one thing.

320
00:16:58,110 --> 00:16:59,820
What did you do after you found out

321
00:17:00,230 --> 00:17:01,230
about this incident?

322
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,270
After watching the video,

323
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:07,030
I did go there to do some fieldwork.

324
00:17:07,030 --> 00:17:08,140
But I didn't dare to probe deeper

325
00:17:08,990 --> 00:17:09,710
because one time

326
00:17:09,710 --> 00:17:10,950
when I pretended to drive by,

327
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:12,910
I was targeted
by several suspected drug traffickers.

328
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:14,470
I realized

329
00:17:14,470 --> 00:17:15,750
it was very dangerous for me.

330
00:17:15,990 --> 00:17:17,580
So I went back to tell Cui Ying

331
00:17:18,380 --> 00:17:19,670
not to tell anyone about this.

332
00:17:20,030 --> 00:17:21,470
We can only pretend it didn't happen.

333
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:24,780
Cui Ying said

334
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:26,860
you mentioned to her before

335
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:28,950
that if someone was killed,

336
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:32,300
just dump the body
at the drug market in Xiaxi District.

337
00:17:33,710 --> 00:17:34,820
Do you recall saying that?

338
00:17:44,140 --> 00:17:45,430
I'm nice to Cui Ying.

339
00:17:45,510 --> 00:17:46,910
We studied under the same professor.

340
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:49,230
I've always been protecting her.

341
00:17:49,780 --> 00:17:51,300
I don't know why she would say that.

342
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:53,540
It's obviously a joke.

343
00:17:53,540 --> 00:17:54,950
Where were you on the evening of 3 May?

344
00:17:55,030 --> 00:17:56,710
I went to Chengguang Club with my friends.

345
00:17:56,860 --> 00:17:58,380
After that, I returned to the office
to work overtime

346
00:17:58,380 --> 00:17:59,430
and only left late at night.

347
00:17:59,430 --> 00:18:00,270
Where's your office?

348
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:00,950
Wenchang Road.

349
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:02,300
We got a hold of surveillance footage

350
00:18:02,300 --> 00:18:03,710
from Bus Route 34.

351
00:18:04,380 --> 00:18:06,380
He Zongyi, the victim of Case 503,

352
00:18:06,430 --> 00:18:08,060
got off at Wenchang Junction

353
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:09,580
at about 10 PM that day.

354
00:18:09,910 --> 00:18:11,230
He was murdered soon after that.

355
00:18:11,990 --> 00:18:13,670
The killer disposed
of the victim's body in Xiaxi District

356
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:16,100
in an attempt to confuse the investigation.

357
00:18:16,910 --> 00:18:19,140
That happens to be a drug trading market area.

358
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:21,190
What do you have

359
00:18:21,780 --> 00:18:22,910
to say about this?

360
00:18:39,990 --> 00:18:41,990
He got off at Wenchang Junction.

361
00:18:48,670 --> 00:18:49,470
What happened after?

362
00:18:51,100 --> 00:18:52,710
What happened during the time
between getting off the bus

363
00:18:52,710 --> 00:18:53,620
and his murder?

364
00:18:53,710 --> 00:18:54,860
You don't even know anything,

365
00:18:55,100 --> 00:18:55,750
right?

366
00:19:00,430 --> 00:19:01,750
You have nothing.

367
00:19:03,340 --> 00:19:04,470
You tried to trick me

368
00:19:04,470 --> 00:19:06,060
into turning myself in with one joke

369
00:19:06,060 --> 00:19:07,540
and one unreliable surveillance footage.

370
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:12,780
Captain Luo,

371
00:19:13,540 --> 00:19:16,060
don't you think you guys
are rather sloppy in your investigation?

372
00:19:19,820 --> 00:19:21,620
They say those in the SID

373
00:19:23,190 --> 00:19:25,230
are Xinzhou's most elite detectives

374
00:19:25,990 --> 00:19:27,750
and the last hope for Xinzhou.

375
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:31,030
I don't think what's so special about it.

376
00:19:58,470 --> 00:20:00,470
It's not much longer until my release.

377
00:20:00,910 --> 00:20:02,710
I don't think
you have any further questions, right?

378
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:04,580
Can I leave earlier?

379
00:20:07,060 --> 00:20:07,950
If I can't,

380
00:20:07,950 --> 00:20:09,190
you can lend me a bed.

381
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:10,860
I need to lie down for a while.

382
00:20:26,270 --> 00:20:28,100
[One hour until release]

383
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:30,270
Where's Qiao?

384
00:20:31,270 --> 00:20:32,620
Captain Luo sent her out.

385
00:20:32,860 --> 00:20:33,540
Where to?

386
00:20:33,580 --> 00:20:34,860
She said she was looking for evidence.

387
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:39,340
Captain Luo, just a reminder.

388
00:20:40,060 --> 00:20:41,910
Not everyone

389
00:20:41,910 --> 00:20:43,230
will be intimidated

390
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:44,430
by your outdated interrogation techniques.

391
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:46,710
Don't be too presumptuous.

392
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:04,510
Zhou Fengnian,

393
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:07,100
don't be too presumptuous.

394
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:15,990
Those collections

395
00:21:15,990 --> 00:21:17,060
on the 13th floor of Chengguang Club

396
00:21:18,030 --> 00:21:19,580
are waiting for your return.

397
00:21:24,540 --> 00:21:25,750
Can you explain

398
00:21:26,580 --> 00:21:27,910
why the paper bag

399
00:21:27,910 --> 00:21:29,750
that He Zongyi held before his death

400
00:21:30,470 --> 00:21:32,510
was in your private collection?

401
00:22:16,780 --> 00:22:17,380
Search!

402
00:22:17,780 --> 00:22:18,380
Yes, ma'am!

403
00:22:35,600 --> 00:22:38,120
[Her secret]

404
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:40,400
[University]

405
00:22:40,450 --> 00:22:42,820
[Internship]

406
00:22:49,920 --> 00:22:55,100
[Freedom]

407
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:13,950
(Fire! Fire!)

408
00:23:20,670 --> 00:23:21,340
Mr. Tao,

409
00:23:21,620 --> 00:23:23,670
Zhou Hongchuan is such a terrible man.

410
00:23:23,820 --> 00:23:25,910
He rented a building in Chengguang Club

411
00:23:26,140 --> 00:23:27,620
as if he's obsessed with collections.

412
00:23:27,620 --> 00:23:29,750
[Freedom]
How could he collect all these?

413
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:30,820
He kept that sleeve as his collection too.

414
00:23:30,860 --> 00:23:32,670
This place is practically an evidence depot.

415
00:23:33,670 --> 00:23:35,380
It seems he asked Cui Ying to meet him there

416
00:23:36,030 --> 00:23:37,710
because he regards her as one of the trophies

417
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:38,860
of the collection.

418
00:23:39,750 --> 00:23:40,860
Zhou Hongchuan

419
00:23:41,060 --> 00:23:42,300
sure is proud and conceited.

420
00:23:43,030 --> 00:23:45,030
Have you found He Zongyi's belonging
from the collection?

421
00:23:46,860 --> 00:23:47,540
Yes.

422
00:23:47,850 --> 00:23:51,250
[Trash]

423
00:23:54,430 --> 00:23:55,820
Lan Qiao just found

424
00:23:55,820 --> 00:23:57,470
the collection belonging to He Zongyi.

425
00:23:57,670 --> 00:23:58,860
Why did Captain Luo...

426
00:24:00,470 --> 00:24:01,710
Captain Luo was tricking him?

427
00:24:02,300 --> 00:24:04,580
Ninety percent of the investigation relies on
evidence and ten percent of it depends on speculation.

428
00:24:05,340 --> 00:24:06,710
Zhou Hongchuan was so confident

429
00:24:06,990 --> 00:24:07,950
that we couldn't find

430
00:24:07,950 --> 00:24:09,340
Chengguang Club.

431
00:24:09,990 --> 00:24:11,430
When he's most proud,

432
00:24:11,430 --> 00:24:12,860
telling him the key evidence

433
00:24:13,670 --> 00:24:15,470
can directly crush his psychological defense.

434
00:24:21,270 --> 00:24:22,470
What 13th floor?

435
00:24:24,190 --> 00:24:25,190
What do you mean?

436
00:24:27,060 --> 00:24:27,820
I don't get it.

437
00:24:29,270 --> 00:24:30,380
Are you saying those aren't yours

438
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:31,510
and they have nothing to do with you?

439
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:33,270
Mr. Zhou,

440
00:24:33,950 --> 00:24:35,340
with so many private collections,

441
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:37,750
will it be difficult to trace your DNA?

442
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:39,820
Besides,

443
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:41,620
who told you

444
00:24:42,820 --> 00:24:44,620
we couldn't find He Zongyi

445
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:45,860
after he left the bus stop

446
00:24:46,710 --> 00:24:48,340
at Wenchang Junction?

447
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:51,910
Impossible.

448
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:54,190
You are suspected of intentional murder
and disposing of the body.

449
00:24:54,190 --> 00:24:55,750
You were afraid
the victim's family would recognize you.

450
00:24:55,750 --> 00:24:57,300
So you lured and coerced an innocent woman

451
00:24:57,300 --> 00:24:58,380
to commit suicide in public.

452
00:24:58,380 --> 00:24:59,750
You even damaged the protective fence.

453
00:24:59,750 --> 00:25:00,820
You intervened and misled

454
00:25:00,820 --> 00:25:01,910
the SID's investigation time and time again

455
00:25:01,910 --> 00:25:03,380
and framed someone else.

456
00:25:04,430 --> 00:25:05,230
Zhou Hongchuan,

457
00:25:05,860 --> 00:25:07,300
we have concrete evidence.

458
00:25:08,670 --> 00:25:10,230
So do you have anything else to say now?

459
00:25:19,430 --> 00:25:21,470
You arrived here without anything

460
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:24,510
and worked so hard for many years.

461
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:26,860
You've finally made something of yourself

462
00:25:26,860 --> 00:25:28,510
and are dating a wealthy girl.

463
00:25:29,270 --> 00:25:30,950
You almost had it all.

464
00:25:31,340 --> 00:25:32,580
But with one wrong step,

465
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:35,060
you became a murderer.

466
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:37,780
If it's meant to be, it will happen eventually.

467
00:25:38,100 --> 00:25:39,950
If it's not meant to be, don't force it.

468
00:25:40,270 --> 00:25:41,060
Zhou Fengnian,

469
00:25:41,540 --> 00:25:43,060
you look pathetic.

470
00:25:43,380 --> 00:25:44,430
You can't call this evidence.

471
00:25:44,430 --> 00:25:45,340
Do you have a video of me murdering anyone?

472
00:25:45,340 --> 00:25:46,750
Are my fingerprints on the paper bag?

473
00:25:46,950 --> 00:25:48,620
Zhang Donglan's fingerprints were visible

474
00:25:48,620 --> 00:25:50,100
over the bloodstains on the tie.

475
00:25:50,100 --> 00:25:51,540
Isn't that more direct evidence?

476
00:25:51,910 --> 00:25:53,300
Is it just because his family is rich,

477
00:25:53,300 --> 00:25:54,270
or is it because he doesn't...

478
00:26:10,430 --> 00:26:11,860
Did you say Zhang Donglan's fingerprints

479
00:26:12,820 --> 00:26:14,380
were visible over the bloodstains

480
00:26:14,380 --> 00:26:15,910
on the tie?

481
00:26:19,270 --> 00:26:19,950
Mr. Zhou,

482
00:26:21,380 --> 00:26:23,030
you're even better

483
00:26:23,030 --> 00:26:23,950
than our forensic team.

484
00:26:25,030 --> 00:26:27,100
It will take them quite some time to find that as they
have to use the equipment to compare the fingerprints.

485
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:30,430
But you could know that
just based on subjective speculation.

486
00:26:38,620 --> 00:26:39,510
Suspect.

487
00:26:40,990 --> 00:26:42,580
So can I address you as a suspect now,

488
00:26:42,990 --> 00:26:43,750
Mr. Zhou?

489
00:26:49,990 --> 00:26:50,670
Cuff him.

490
00:27:00,510 --> 00:27:01,860
We have confirmed that he committed the crime.

491
00:27:02,510 --> 00:27:04,230
The rest are just some minor details.

492
00:27:04,950 --> 00:27:06,430
I won't be wasting my time here with you anymore.

493
00:27:06,990 --> 00:27:07,750
Wait!

494
00:27:09,820 --> 00:27:10,950
It was self-defense.

495
00:27:14,670 --> 00:27:15,910
What did you say, Mr. Zhou?

496
00:27:19,670 --> 00:27:20,820
I acted in self-defense.

497
00:27:21,820 --> 00:27:23,100
You are a legal industry elite

498
00:27:23,100 --> 00:27:24,470
who has received professional legal education.

499
00:27:25,270 --> 00:27:26,540
Do you consider the situation

500
00:27:26,540 --> 00:27:27,710
a legitimate defense?

501
00:27:27,910 --> 00:27:29,820
Did you suffer a rebound in your head

502
00:27:29,860 --> 00:27:31,340
when you struck He Zongyi's head with a stick?

503
00:27:31,340 --> 00:27:32,950
He Zongyi was suspected of drug trafficking.

504
00:27:36,060 --> 00:27:37,100
I was compelled

505
00:27:38,380 --> 00:27:39,670
to do it.

506
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:50,060
I know you're investigating Chen Yuan's case.

507
00:27:50,140 --> 00:27:51,910
I can appear as the main witness.

508
00:27:53,950 --> 00:27:55,270
I can cooperate with your investigation.

509
00:27:55,990 --> 00:27:57,100
As long as you agree

510
00:28:00,470 --> 00:28:02,100
to reduce my sentence.

511
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:51,580
Zhou Hongchuan,

512
00:28:52,230 --> 00:28:53,510
I've reported this to Chief Du.

513
00:28:54,430 --> 00:28:55,860
We did what you asked too.

514
00:28:57,030 --> 00:28:58,140
So can you tell us now?

515
00:29:00,990 --> 00:29:02,060
At the end of last year,

516
00:29:03,060 --> 00:29:05,340
as a legal consultant, I took the team

517
00:29:05,580 --> 00:29:07,190
to Xiaxi District to meet our client.

518
00:29:08,820 --> 00:29:10,780
We didn't drive because we were planning to drink.

519
00:29:12,670 --> 00:29:14,670
I encountered someone who was following me

520
00:29:16,380 --> 00:29:17,710
when I was waiting for a taxi after the gathering.

521
00:29:18,950 --> 00:29:20,430
Was it He Zongyi?

522
00:29:22,750 --> 00:29:23,910
He recognized me.

523
00:29:24,910 --> 00:29:26,340
He blackmailed me. Asking for 100,000 yuan.

524
00:29:45,340 --> 00:29:46,540
Is this Mandheling?

525
00:29:49,710 --> 00:29:50,780
It would've tasted better

526
00:29:51,100 --> 00:29:52,950
if the water temperature
had been two degrees lower when brewing.

527
00:30:08,990 --> 00:30:10,470
(He came on his own)

528
00:30:10,620 --> 00:30:12,380
(and deliberately showed up nearby my office.)

529
00:30:13,230 --> 00:30:13,990
(With no other options,)

530
00:30:13,990 --> 00:30:15,470
(I could only try to appease him for the time being.)

531
00:30:16,340 --> 00:30:17,580
(So I asked him to meet me)

532
00:30:17,580 --> 00:30:18,670
(at the coffee shop downstairs from my office.)

533
00:30:41,470 --> 00:30:42,510
This is Mandheling.

534
00:30:43,910 --> 00:30:44,780
I know.

535
00:30:44,860 --> 00:30:45,820
When I delivered the goods,

536
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:46,860
I saw this name.

537
00:30:48,230 --> 00:30:48,990
Fengnian,

538
00:30:49,230 --> 00:30:50,950
I'm working at a coffee shop now.

539
00:30:51,230 --> 00:30:52,300
Do you like this coffee?

540
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:53,190
Do you want some?

541
00:30:53,270 --> 00:30:54,670
I can get them at a lower price.

542
00:30:56,100 --> 00:30:57,030
It's okay. Thanks.

543
00:31:04,510 --> 00:31:05,310
Fengnian,

544
00:31:05,620 --> 00:31:07,310
you're doing pretty well

545
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:08,550
in Xinzhou.

546
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:09,820
I'm really happy for you.

547
00:31:12,420 --> 00:31:12,990
By the way,

548
00:31:12,990 --> 00:31:13,900
I thought

549
00:31:13,900 --> 00:31:16,070
I saw you with a girl several days ago.

550
00:31:17,310 --> 00:31:19,510
Was that your girlfriend?

551
00:31:23,100 --> 00:31:23,900
What do you want?

552
00:31:25,340 --> 00:31:27,070
I'm just asking.

553
00:31:27,580 --> 00:31:28,900
Your parents

554
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:30,340
would feel relieved

555
00:31:30,380 --> 00:31:31,790
to see how well you do now.

556
00:31:31,860 --> 00:31:33,470
He Zongyi, don't bring this up.

557
00:31:36,230 --> 00:31:37,310
Since high school,

